            <div type="transcript" id="F1253A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Risk is the Hair<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 that holds the Tun </l>
                    <l>Seductive in the Air - </l>
                    <l>That Tun is hollow -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 but the Tun - </l>
                    <l>With Hundred<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Weights - to spare - </l>
                    <l>Too ponderous to <app type="emendation"><lem>sus - &lt;app type=&quot;division&quot;&gt;&lt;lem&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;/lem&gt;&lt;/app&gt;
 pect</lem><rdg>suspect</rdg></app>
 the snare</l>
                    <l>Espies that fickle<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 chair </l>
                    <l>And<add type="alternate" extent="seats itself to be let go">mounts to be to atoms hurled -</add>
 seats itself<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to be let go </l>
                    <l>By that perfidious<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Hair - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The &quot;foolish Tun&quot; the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Critics say - </l>
                    <l>While that<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="delusive">obliging - &amp;#x2022; enchanting -</add>
 delusive<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Hair</l>
                    <l><app type="emendation"><lem>Per &lt;app type=&quot;division&quot;&gt;&lt;lem&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;/lem&gt;&lt;/app&gt;
 - suasive&lt;app type=&quot;division&quot;&gt;&lt;lem&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;/lem&gt;&lt;/app&gt;
 </lem><rdg>Persuasive</rdg></app>
 as Perdition, </l>
                    <l>Decoys <app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
it's<add type="alternate" extent="Traveller">Passenger</add>
 Traveller </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
